resources.string: "Datos: Data: Cali is a Colombian city located in the department of Valle del Cauca. It is known for the salsa dance. Some tourist sites in Cali are: Cristo Rey, Cali Zoo, La tertulia Museum, La Ermita Church, San Antonio Church. Surface: 564 km², Elevation: 1,018 m, Foundation: July 25, 1536, Mayor: Jorge Iván Ospina, Population: 2,228 million (2018), Time: 26 ° C, wind from the W at 13 km / h, humidity from 68 %"
